reviews.text:
Do you hear that? In the distance? It's the ice cream man!&#xD;
Absolute banger of a recipe. Smooth cinnamon, rich buttery ice cream and a mellow, full apple. It truly ticks all the boxes. Even mtl this liquid is perfectly balanced and complex enough to keep staying interesting. &#xD;
&#xD;
Full disclosure, I didn't use rich cinnamon, though I can only imagine it improves with it.&#xD;
&#xD;
Speaking of improve, I vastly preferred this after a week steep. &#xD;
&#xD;
Seriously, go mix this. And order three times as much lb vic as you think you need. Trust me.
